Yesu kawalongela Wayahudi wowamkundile kawalongela, "Wone mikale mwii mbuli zangu, mweye mwiza kuwa wanahina wangu kweli.
Maabaho muizela kukomya, nayo kukomya kowalekeni mweye milejehe.
Wamwidika, "Cheye twa ivyazi da Abulahamu, na hatuwa wapogozi wa munhu yoyose. Vino vino vinoga vinoga vinoga? " 'Mowa milejehe.' "
